StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
@ID uniqueidentifier
AS
BEGIN
SET TRANSACTION ISOLATION LEVEL READ UNCOMMITTED
SELECT count(*) as TotalCount FROM [USMC].[Evalua.onChecklist] WHERE DateCer..ed IS NULL AND Mul.MonthEvalua.onId = @ID
END
